Veteran actress Patience Ozokwor has declared Nollywood legend Olu Jacob is irreplaceable. She spoke at the 80th celebration of the screen icon last Sunday where top Nollywood acts gathered to celebrate their living legend. Ozokwor complimented her senior colleague’s topnotch acting skills adding, she misses him alongside his versatility on set.   Yul Edochie carpets FG for Kuje prison attacks     Mercy Aigbe prays for daughter on 21     Yomi Fabiyi, Baby mama in war of words over alleged…   “I’m missing him on set, he can play an Igbo king, he can play a Yoruba king, in fact, I don’t think anybody can replace him,” she said. Joke Silva in November 2021 disclosed that her husband was battling dementia with lewy bodies (DLB). Jacob’s wife said he had been managing the condition for a couple of years.